"69:7:11" : {s: 69, a: 7, w: 11, r: "صرع", t: "صَرْعَىٰ", l: "صَرْعَىٰ", lc: 1, tl: "ṣarʿā", lb: "আছাড়, ধরাশয়ী",e: "fallen", b: "লুটিয়ে পড়ে আছে", f: 1, rm: "to stick down, prostrate, fling. saraa - lying or thrown prostrate, fallen down."},
